<item>
            <title>[HBASE-3544] list all current active settings</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-3544</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It would be very handy to have a way to see all effective settings for a running hbase cluster (shell or webinterface) so that one can see them in one go. Similar to the jobconf overview one gets in the jobtracker of map/reduce&lt;/p&gt;</description>
